title: Report format
body:
<Report Format>
1) Detailed activities that the contributors have performed.
2) Any supportive materials that prove their activities.
3) BSC wallet address for the GRANT reward

<Action Settings on Snapshot>
* Two choices must be added: "For" and "Against"
* Single choice voting
* Start Date: yesterday
* End Date: 7 days from now
* Leave the block number as default
author: 0xe1aAF39DB1Cd7E16C4305410Fe72B13c7ADD17e6
